                            Featured Article Title
                        </h1>
                        <p class="article-abstract" style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; color: #4A4A4A;">
                            Brief summary of the article goes here.
                        </p>
                        <div class="article-meta">
                            <span class="date" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; color: #6D6D6D;">Created on: 01/01/2024</span>
                            <span class="viewcount" style="color: #9A9A9A;">
                                <i class="fa fa-eye"></i> 1234 views
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary" style="background-color: #1E90FF; color: white;">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Right Column: Sidebar -->
                <div class="col-lg-4">
